&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with product usage data or product-led growth signals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in expansion and NRR-focused programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with developer or technical customer bases.&lt;/li&gt;
