&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll help evolve systems that process trillions of transactions each month, with a focus on reliability, performance, observability, and operational excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Engineers on the Core team own services from development through production operations, including monitoring, incident response, and capacity planning.&lt;/p&gt;
