&lt;li&gt;Improve system reliability and operational resilience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own services from development through production operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create metrics, dashboards, alerts, and runbooks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support incident response and capacity planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize latency, throughput, and system performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work across cloud infrastructure and data systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools thoughtfully to improve engineering workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
