&lt;li&gt;Focus initially on one to two strategic industries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and own the &quot;Real-Time Infrastructure for AI&quot; positioning and messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create sales and event enablement materials, including decks, one-pagers, talk tracks, and competitive messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Developer Relations (DevRel) and Product to ensure messaging is grounded in verifiable proof.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Equip account-based and field marketing campaigns with tailored messaging for target accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test buyer-language naming and iterate based on what resonates and converts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product and Legal to keep messaging accurate and on-claim.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
