&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years in B2B product or solutions marketing for technical or developer-focused software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of developing positioning and messaging that improved pipeline quality or conversion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to translate technical capabilities into buyer-focused outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative, self-directed, and comfortable partnering across Sales, DevRel, and Product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
